revision.text: Possibly: Hē tou Hērodotou Halikarnasseōs historia. = Herodoti Halicarnassensis historia : ex editione Jacobi Gronovii; tomis novem : adjectus est, ex eadem editione, liber de vita Homeri; vulgo sed falso, adscriptus Herodoto. (Herodotus; Jacobus Gronovius). 9v. (Glasguae : In aedibus Academicis excudebant Robertus et Andreas Foulis, Academiae typographi, MDCCLXI [1761]). http://library.st-andrews.ac.uk/record=b1887894~S1
